---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Meter Access Points | Blue Cap IT — Meter Partner" description="Meter Wi-Fi 7 access points deliver blazing-fast wireless with tri-band radios and custom circuitry. The A1 for high-demand offices and A2 for hospitality — fully managed as a service.">
  <div class="inner-hero">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <img src="/meter/Meter-purple.png" alt="Meter" style="max-height:60px;width:auto;margin-bottom:1.5rem;"/>
      <div class="crumbs"><a href="index.html">Home</a> <span>/</span> <a href="meter.html">Networking</a> <span>/</span> Access Points</div>
      <div class="section-label">Meter Hardware</div>
      <h1>Meter <span class="grad">Access Points</span></h1>
      <p class="section-sub">Wi-Fi 7 tri-band access points with custom-designed circuitry for strict radio isolation between 5 GHz and 6 GHz bands. Blazing-fast wireless performance, purpose-built by Meter and fully managed as part of your network subscription.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- AP MODELS -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div style="text-align:center;max-width:640px;margin:0 auto 2rem;">
        <div class="section-label">Access Point Lineup</div>
        <h2>Wi-Fi 7. <span class="grad">Built by Meter.</span></h2>
        <p class="section-sub" style="margin:0.8rem auto 0;text-align:center;">Two access points designed for different environments — both delivering the latest Wi-Fi 7 standard with industry-leading performance.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        <img src="/meter/hw-a-series.avif" alt="Meter Access Points" style="max-width:600px;width:100%;border-radius:0.75rem;" />
      </div>
      <div class="products-grid" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr));max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;">
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon">📶</div>
          <h3>A1 — Premium Indoor AP</h3>
          <p>The A1 is Meter's premium access point, designed for high-demand indoor environments where performance is critical. Conference rooms, open offices, co-working spaces, and trading floors.</p>
          <ul style="margin-top:1rem;padding-left:1.2rem;font-size:0.92rem;color:var(--muted);">
            <li>Wi-Fi 7 (802.11be) tri-band</li>
            <li>2.4 GHz + 5 GHz + 6 GHz radios</li>
            <li>Custom circuitry for strict band isolation</li>
            <li>High-density device support</li>
            <li>PoE powered via Meter switches</li>
            <li>Cloud-managed with zero-touch provisioning</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon">📶</div>
          <h3>A2 — Hospitality AP</h3>
          <p>The A2 delivers the same Wi-Fi 7 performance as the A1 in a form factor designed for hospitality environments. Hotels, restaurants, lobbies, and guest-facing spaces where aesthetics and simple installation matter.</p>
          <ul style="margin-top:1rem;padding-left:1.2rem;font-size:0.92rem;color:var(--muted);">
            <li>Wi-Fi 7 (802.11be) tri-band</li>
            <li>Same performance as A1</li>
            <li>Optimized for hospitality deployments</li>
            <li>Simplified installation</li>
            <li>Guest network isolation built-in</li>
            <li>Seamless roaming across APs</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FEATURES -->
  <section style="background:var(--surface);">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="section-label">Why Meter Access Points</div>
          <h2>Faster. Smarter. <span class="grad">Fully Managed.</span></h2>
          <p class="section-sub">Meter's access points aren't just faster — they're smarter. Custom circuitry ensures strict isolation between 5 GHz and 6 GHz radios, eliminating the interference that plagues other Wi-Fi 7 access points. And because Meter manages your entire network, your APs are always optimized, updated, and performing at their peak.</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="why-list">
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">⚡</div>
            <div><h4>Wi-Fi 7 Performance</h4><p>The latest wireless standard delivers dramatically faster speeds, lower latency, and better performance in crowded environments compared to Wi-Fi 6/6E.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">🔬</div>
            <div><h4>Custom Radio Isolation</h4><p>Meter's proprietary circuitry design ensures strict isolation between 5 GHz and 6 GHz bands — eliminating cross-band interference for cleaner, faster connections.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">🔄</div>
            <div><h4>Seamless Roaming</h4><p>Move between floors and zones without drops. Meter's software coordinates handoffs between APs so devices stay connected as people move through your space.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">📊</div>
            <div><h4>Real-Time Analytics</h4><p>See connected devices, signal strength, channel utilization, and client health — all in real time through the Meter Dashboard.</p></div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-inner" style="text-align:center;padding:4rem 1.5rem;">
      <h2>Ready for <span class="grad">Wi-Fi 7?</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub" style="max-width:600px;margin:0.8rem auto 2rem;text-align:center;">Contact Blue Cap IT for a wireless assessment. We'll evaluate your current Wi-Fi coverage and show you how Meter's access points can transform your wireless experience.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Assessment</a>
        <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost">Call (410) 858-4031</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
